getReferencePrice.t.sol
├── given price data is not registered for the provided base token
│  └── it should revert with PriceFeedRouteNotRegistered
└── given price data is registered for the providedbase token
   ├── given one of the feed prices is negative
   │  └── it should revert with NegativeTokenPrice
   └── given all feed prices are non-negative
      ├── given one of the feed price ages exceeds the staleness threshold 
      │  └── it should revert with PriceFeedStale
      └── given none of the feed price ages exceed the staleness threshold
         └── it should return the price of base token expressed in reference currency, according to aggregated price feed route
         